    <releases>
        <release version="2021.8.14-treviso" date="2021-08-14">
          <description>
            <p>News</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Toggle the last Update date in the bottles list</li>
                <li>Fallback the working directory to the executable path if it fails to run</li>
                <li>Now a visual feedback is provided when a download fail the checksum validation</li>
                <li>Wine support for Wayland trought XWayland</li>
                <li>Support for 32-bit bottles with custom environment</li>
                <li>Removed colors from the environments in the bottle creation as these can be interpreted as suggested actions</li>
                <li>Now the user can only install one dependency per time to avoid conflicts</li>
                <li>Now the Crash Report dialog display similar reports before send a new one</li>
                <li>Now it is possible to clone a bottle with a new name, this can also be used for bottles templating</li>
                <li>The Bottles version is now provided in the Crash report</li>
                <li>Reduced the Flatpak permissions</li>
                <li>You can now choose a custom working directory for each bottle</li>
                <li>You can see a new button in the bottle details with a folder icon, this helps you expose new directories to Bottles</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Bug fixes</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Fixed a bug in the detection of broken bottles</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug that was causing a File Not Found error with broken downloads</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug that make Bottles crash when the user goes offline during a download</li>
                <li>Same as the above but this handle downloads with wrong sizes than the source</li>
                <li>Fixed the File Manager integration in Flatpak</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug that make Bottles crash when fail in name resolution during a download</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug in temp directory clean up</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug that make Bottles crash when the Update Date is not set in the bottle</li>
                <li>Fixed a bug in bottle configuration upgrade that was causing a loop</li>
            </ul>

